comments: Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact with Barton's (DEN) backside as he makes the pass.
Simmons (PHI) is drawn into the air towards Harris (DEN) on the pump fake and initiates contact with Harris' body during his upward shooting motion.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Embiid's (PHI) body as he receives the pass, causing him to briefly lose control of the ball, which he quickly recovers.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal body contact with Embiid (PHI) after he re-gains control of the ball and backs down Jokic in the post.
Barton (DEN) makes marginal contact with Horford's (PHI) right arm at the end of the drive.
Barton (DEN) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) shot attempt near the rim and doesn't make arm or body contact.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact with Jokic's (DEN) backside before cleanly deflecting the pass attempt.
Millsap (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Thybulle's (PHI) path and does not deliver the contact.
Embiid (PHI) moves alongside Barton's (DEN) path as Barton initiates the incidental contact during his driving shot attempt.
Horford (PHI) cleanly dislodges the ball from Barton (DEN) during his driving shot attempt.
Harris (DEN) makes marginal contact with Harris' (PHI) left arm after he picks up his dribble along the lane line.
Barton (DEN) makes marginal contact with Simmons' (PHI) left hip as they go over the pick and as Simmons simultaneously runs into his teammate's side.
Simmons (PHI) attempts to pass around Barton (DEN) and the ball deflects off his thigh.
Horford (PHI) makes incidental contact with Millsap's (DEN) right leg as he simultaneously cleanly strips Millsap of the ball.

After Millsap (DEN) controls the ball and has it dislodged, Simmons (PHI) dives on the floor and makes contact with the ball. The tap into the backcourt is not a controlled pass, which means neither team maintains possession, and thus allows Harris (PHI) the ability to legally gather the ball.
Harris (DEN) makes marginal contact with Horford's (PHI) front after the release of his jump shot attempt and doesn't affect his ability to follow-through naturally.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Horford (PHI) makes marginal contact with Harris (DEN) during the inbound.
Thybulle (PHI) cleanly deflects the inbound pass intended for Jokic (DEN).
Horford (PHI) wraps Grant's (DEN) midsection and affects his FOM during the inbound.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact as he contests Jokic's (DEN) driving shot attempt.
Grant (DEN) commits the take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Grant (DEN) commits the take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Embiid (PHI) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Grant (DEN) makes marginal contact with Embiid's (PHI) right arm.
